this_title: Damien Power: Alone in the Crowd
introduction: Multi award winning comedian Damien Power debuts his first special shot at the iconic Corner Hotel in Melbourne, Australia.Why was Jesus so popular? What has created this new generation of hyper-sexual environmentalists? Why does my Ex’s new husband continue to lie? Watch this electric debut hour and add more confusion to your life.Strap in for an electric night of comedy from one of the best!
